{"tid":1879391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【避炎囤糧好推介】瑞和街48年老字號 必買懷舊南乳餅乾＋麥芽糖馬仔","createTime":"2020-02-14T07:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T09:52:33.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"691dc1808a5e819fea2b08e55627e15c4c6b79c4","tid":1879391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/3kLLc_jo7eOyZwEI2EIcOcA8Dl8GKhAOLaGHk6vpirnF6-CJwCUOnc6MvI6-RTRw2Hj7qYZudJ3jPbOeus3jKPtoXcgHPK9uXFaktmHQQ5ieLhvda0L2T6tprD8PxXYUiDoCqbu4sP2gA_oTOiJYDR_eVMicxY9vA7MxJc_OKyY5jzD0aEi2dOWyzpbSWB0X9Lf6SLWTOFF0IGFnqUwWEW3SOiiJ7AaFu4xd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F3kLLc_jo7eOyZwEI2EIcOcA8Dl8GKhAOLaGHk6vpirnF6-CJwCUOnc6MvI6-RTRw2Hj7qYZudJ3jPbOeus3jKPtoXcgHPK9uXFaktmHQQ5ieLhvda0L2T6tprD8PxXYUiDoCqbu4sP2gA_oTOiJYDR_eVMicxY9vA7MxJc_OKyY5jzD0aEi2dOWyzpbSWB0X9Lf6SLWTOFF0IGFnqUwWEW3SOiiJ7AaFu4xd&h=062d8012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XTHVUGTKWURZNV7NC42G76FATA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXTHVUGTKWURZNV7NC42G76FATA.jpg&h=f491e2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肺炎疫情日益嚴重，市民人心惶惶，四出搶購糧食，口罩、白米、乾糧。最壞的時刻，分外懷念舊時的好。全條街都是魚油雜貨店的觀塘瑞和街中，就有間小店，生意因疫情而好了不少，不少街坊來掃貨買乾糧，「最近不知道是因為疫情的問題還是怎樣，人們不想外出用餐，<span style=\"color: red;\">這些餅乾可作乾糧，所以一有疫情就會被搶購一空。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n店舖開業48年，傳至第二代，現年65歲的老闆黃文金早年亦想過退休。「業主加租，我都決定退休了。但後來街坊要求，希望我能保留下來，繼續賣馬仔和懷舊食品，因此即使要捱貴租，我都決定留下來，再做多幾年，希望能做到七十一歲吧。」<br />\n<br />\n「由我父親接手時，店裏已經開始有餅乾賣。」舖面放滿的一包包懷舊餅乾，是不少人兒時最愛。「那時候賣餅乾很有趣，既有零售，又可以用啤酒瓶換餅乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，那時只要帶一個空瓶來換已經可以換到幾塊餅乾。」可惜餅廠行業式微，黃老闆見證六七間餅廠，逐間因不同原因倒閉，香港現在只剩下一間大地餅廠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/IMPQ6NRVQTHDKTJMT25MQU6J2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FIMPQ6NRVQTHDKTJMT25MQU6J2I.jpg&h=1f3c97fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/QUC3ZDMMAYRHL7BMZ4BFUIUUQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQUC3ZDMMAYRHL7BMZ4BFUIUUQ4.jpg&h=f3c747d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n採訪期間，不少街坊熟客陸續來光顧，一個月來兩三次的熟客陳小姐笑指自己昨天已來了一次﹕「但賣光了，沒有貨，今天再來，女兒叫我來買，她很喜歡吃馬仔及南乳餅。」店內有售近十款懷舊餅乾，蛋白花占餅、鳳梨夾心餅，不少市面少見，如果初次來買，最推介椒鹽南乳餅（$20/包），一包餅乾內藏數款形狀，咬落脆口，帶有南乳鹹香。<br />\n<img src=\"https://arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/MP2ED7CUNBTQ2RV36T3KRDB2AQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FMP2ED7CUNBTQ2RV36T3KRDB2AQ.jpg&h=13cb88c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一招牌貨是麥芽馬仔，$28一包四件，均是來自香港順香園。<span style=\"color: red;\">這款麥芽馬仔是唯一在香港製造的馬仔，跟大陸或台灣做的馬仔是完全不同的，真正用麥芽糖製造</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，拉開後，可見絲絲金黃糖膠，嚐起來黏口煙韌，齒頰留香。"},{"pid":"2ae86122316a91d2ff0b6653fbc2ce6aaef94bee","tid":1879391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"觀塘舊樓單位爆屎渠3天 屎水浸走廊 正面播毒瑞和街市政大廈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQxKxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQxKxS</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】流鶯猖獗瑞和街惹播毒隱憂 街坊恐引社區爆發<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1859154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1859154</a>"},{"pid":"b9fb9d087c0bdb6bfed176582d873e1006509ff2","tid":1879391,"uid":145837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"嘉頓雜餅表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcd3ecbd8918bce04dd036ba5a28d4e5637a827","tid":1879391,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"南乳餅乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8b55448067cb4b85f9e52f0a3548778bd363f6","tid":1879391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"房協觀塘花園大廈的「暫租住屋」，開始接受合資格的公屋輪候家庭申請，單位共有<span style=\"color: red;\">20多個</span>，實用面積26至44平方米，月租由1,339元至2,039元，可供輪候公屋3年或以上的3至5人家庭申請，下月10日截止申請。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200211/photo/bkn-20200211125854757-0211_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200211135526\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200211%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200211125854757-0211_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200211135526&h=287fd171&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a2139571de18712d1a3dcfcb4461d757b27039d","tid":1879391,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"藍定黃"},{"pid":"3546d83a199d46cfaeb4e77171af53762dbf8a25","tid":1879391,"uid":3063,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b9fb9d087c0bdb6bfed176582d873e1006509ff2","tid":1879391,"uid":145837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"嘉頓雜餅表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"大佬<br />\n人地叫乾糧<br />\n你叫軍糧<br />\n唔同級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86187e2e3abd6bb780de230fc0ac0f423945bf00","tid":1879391,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9fb9d087c0bdb6bfed176582d873e1006509ff2","tid":1879391,"uid":145837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"嘉頓雜餅表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\"